還要把這個愛國的道理，想各種辦法，以通俗易懂的語言說給身邊人來聽。我愛國，愛國無罪。歡迎愛國人士留言討論，不愛國的人請不要給我留言。不要忘記，這裡是CHINA，艾木拆膩斯~～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陰陽怪氣"},{"pid":"56c053af45d0640fb855409c7a3536148300c381","tid":2507823,"uid":292987,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d65d38f9d605ad12172d2f61056aa1d265419b0c","tid":2507823,"uid":275912,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"1c32976ded0a9bfd43c86174af909c6bf18832e8","tid":2507823,"uid":249639,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"4913dcafb5871bf0dd1a5c47a23df0dc62fd4b97","tid":2507823,"uid":275912,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得個比喻不倫不類...<br />\n如果係話將中共當成比喻中既壞人<br />\n出生率降低算係不治之症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n佢到底明唔明人係點樣黎<br />\n天讉又係報響邊個身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:11:59.000Z","msg":"人口紅利要還 無勞動力草都慳番<br />\n共產党滅絕 死也含笑<br />\n呢種悲嗚同攬炒一樣異曲同工"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:25:11.000Z","msg":"中共唔限制生仔既話<br />\n人口好快回到血<br />\n<br />\n等佢自己爆煲好唔現實<br />\n打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T18:05:25.000Z","msg":"訓咗幾耐<br />\n咪話限制 求人生仔都冇人生啦而家"},{"pid":"a2a9a083f76022e6f4bc0257618b3cb46bc2ea6f","tid":2507823,"uid":333376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T18:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/InoriChyan/status/1387245360049909765?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FInoriChyan%2Fstatus%2F1387245360049909765%3Fs%3D09&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0olFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=b9effd60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FInoriChyan%2Fstatus%2F1387245360049909765%3Fs%3D09&h=2