ihu.com%2Fquestion%2F456600186&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0olFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=200f0d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/456600186</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EsZvTQp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEsZvTQp.jpg&h=2ec7f544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等睇黨安法新秩序下港共點樣超支超俄領先全球引入強制生育<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"港女以後小心啦<br />\n之後港共分分鐘狗急跳牆玩強制交配強制配對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:06:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得強国班窮鬼會不斷生"},{"pid":"0a648c99b99649508396989dbe79ef95b8397167","tid":2507823,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f374f91ef966e71f5c3cc930d9fc32560d68bac7","tid":2507823,"uid":292987,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"f922beb3d071bbf5a3710705a44adcd7931c6aa7","tid":2507823,"uid":249639,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://botanwang.com/articles/202104/为什么看到出生率降低觉得很爽.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbotanwang.com%2Farticles%2F202104%2F%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E5%87%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%8E%87%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E8%A7%89%E5%BE%97%E5%BE%88%E7%88%BD.html&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0olFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=fb2ece26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://botanwang.com/articles/202104/为什么看到出生率降低觉得很爽.html</a>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:59:10.000Z","msg":"經驗加3告辭：我一開始也覺得很爽，只是後來覺得還遠遠不夠，就是還不夠爽的意思。另外，我必須說明的是，不婚不育是愛國的表現。為什麼呢？我給你說說這個道理哈。窮是因為什麼？因為懶，因為不努力，也是因為不聰明。那你想啊，懶的人、不努力的人、不聰明的人。生出來的孩子，那能教育好麼？對吧。會繼承貧窮基因、懶惰基因、笨拙基因的。正所謂&zwnj;&zwnj;「龍生龍、鳳生鳳、老鼠的兒子會打洞&zwnj;&zwnj;」。那末，如果咱們窮人都不婚不育了，剩下生孩子的都是什麼人？就都是精英、富翁們。所以說，只要咱們窮人不結婚，不生育。那等再過幾十年，咱中國，就都是精英的後代，都是富二代了。這不好嗎？所以說，不生孩子，它不僅僅是為的自己減輕責任，更是，為了祖國能夠繁榮昌盛。為了咱們國家全都是聰明的人、富有的人。你看，是不是這麼個理兒？結論顯而易見：不婚不育，是愛國的表現。那麼為什麼說覺得生育率下降還不夠爽呢？這就是說：愛國讓人心情爽朗，但是愛國這件事，又是永無止境的。說是生育率下降，可是下降到這種程度，還不夠，還遠遠不夠。就是這個意思。所以我們不僅僅要以身作則，並且還要把這個愛國的道理，想各種辦法，以通俗易懂的語言說給身邊人來聽。我愛國，愛國無罪。歡迎愛國人士留言討論，不愛國的人請不要給我留言。不要忘記，這裡是CHINA，艾木拆膩斯~～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陰陽怪氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:07:56.000Z","msg":"所以說，只要咱們窮人不結婚，不生育。那等再過幾十年，咱中國，就都是精英的後代，都是富二代了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7616016c773d1c5e811eab4c95516a96f3fc462f","tid":2507823,"uid":79442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:14:44.000Z","msg":"太天真了，到時綁晒d靚女去比領導做肉便器，狂生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醜女就人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"f922beb3d071bbf5a3710705a44adcd7931c6aa7","tid":2507823,"uid":249639,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://botanwang.com/articles/202104/为什么看到出生率降低觉得很爽.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbotanwang.com%2Farticles%2F202104%2F%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E5%87%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%8E%87%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E8%A7%89%E5%BE%97%E5%BE%88%E7%88%BD.html&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0olFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=fb2ece26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://botanwang.com/articles/202104/为什么看到出生率降低觉得很爽.html</a>"}}